  m_text: This will let you choose what main strategy do you want to follow for the
    mechanic. Both <b>NA</b> and <b>EU</b> are identical to the <b>pastebins</b>
    or their respective <b>Hector video</b>. The <b>JP</b> strat is identical to
    the common <b>Game8/Nukemaru</b> strat. <b>Zenith Uptime</b>, <b>Brain Deluxe</b>
    and <b>Emergency Meeting</b> are optional strats that use others as base but
    follow their respective raidplans by default. If you want to practice <b>Banana
    Codex</b>, pick <b>EU</b> and configure the rest of the options below to match
    what <b>Banana Codex</b> uses.
