  m_text: This will let you choose how you want to resolve the Stacks and Defamations
    that are tethered to players.<br><br><b>Hector/Braindead Uptime Idyllic</b> is
    identical to the strategy from <b>Hector's video</b> and from the <b>Brain Deluxe</b>
    strat.<br><br><b>NA</b>, <b>EU</b> and <b>JP</b> strategies use their respective
    PF strats.<br><br><b>Banana Codex</b> is basically a <i>flipped</i> <b>Hector
    Uptime Idyllic</b>, it is also the same strat used by <b>Emergency Meeting</b>,
    but it is not a standard PF strat.
